---
<header class="w-full bg-[#ff6b6b] border-b-4 border-[#2f2f2f] px-8 flex flex-row items-center justify-between shadow-lg h-[100px] box-border">
  <h1 class="text-[#ffffff] text-3xl drop-shadow-[4px_4px_0_#2f2f2f] font-pixel tracking-widest">
    RETRO.LOG
  </h1>
      <div class="flex gap-4">
        <a
        href="/"
        class="/* 1. 基础样式：像素字体、粗边框、背景色 */
    font-pixel text-xs px-4 py-2 bg-[#ff6b6b] text-white border-4 border-[#2f2f2f]
    
    /* 2. 复古阴影：使用自定义的任意值阴影 [x轴 y轴 模糊 扩展 颜色] */
    /* 我们设置 4px 偏移，0 模糊，颜色为深色 */
    shadow-[4px_4px_0_0_#2f2f2f]
    
    /* 3. 交互逻辑：过渡动画 */
    transition-all duration-75
    
    /* 4. 悬停效果：向上微跳 */
    hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-[4px_8px_0_0_#2f2f2f]
    
    /* 5. 按压效果 (核心)：向右下移动 4px，阴影消失 */
    active:translate-x-[4px] active:translate-y-[4px] active:shadow-none"
      >
        HOME
      </a>
      <!-- 关于按钮 (白色) -->
      <a
        href="/about"
        class="font-pixel text-xs px-4 py-2 bg-white text-[#2f2f2f] border-4 border-[#2f2f2f]
    shadow-[4px_4px_0_0_#2f2f2f]
    transition-all duration-75
    hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-[4px_8px_0_0_#2f2f2f]
    active:translate-x-[4px] active:translate-y-[4px] active:shadow-none"
      >
        ABOUT
      </a>
      </div>
</header>

<style>
  .font-pixel {
    font-family: 'Press Start 2P', cursive;
  }
</style>
